column10:
My rating: 69 / 100.
(+) Classic gameplay corresponds to old M&M Heroes;
(+) Map Generator increases a lot replayability;
(+) Campaign's scenarios are quite challenging;
(+) Atmospheric music and ambience sounds;
(–) Dwarves faction is very dissapointing;
(–) The town's interface seem to be boring/unfinish;
(–) Cut scenes are absolutely awful and dull.
